WEBVTT

1
00:01:54.860 --> 00:01:57.317
Yankee-nine-niner,
what are your coordinates?

2
00:01:57.401 --> 00:01:59.650
Zero-two-zero, flight level one-five.

3
00:01:59.735 --> 00:02:02.193
We're above release point Echo-Bravo-one.

4
00:02:02.276 --> 00:02:03.609
Move in and check it out.

5
00:02:03.693 --> 00:02:05.317
Roger. Moving in.

6
00:02:12.818 --> 00:02:17.484
Food riot in progress.
Approximately 1,500 civilians.

7
00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:19.193
No weapons evident.

8
00:02:19.276 --> 00:02:23.026
Proceed with Plan Alpha.
Eliminate anything moving.

9
00:02:23.110 --> 00:02:25.026
I said the crowd is unarmed.

10
00:02:25.110 --> 00:02:26.692
There are lots of women
and children down there.

11
00:02:26.776 --> 00:02:28.358
All they want is food, for God's sake!

12
00:02:28.443 --> 00:02:31.193
As you were, Richards.
Proceed with Plan Alpha.

13
00:02:31.276 --> 00:02:33.193
All rioters must be eliminated.

14
00:02:33.985 --> 00:02:37.525
The hell with you.
I will not fire on helpless people.

15
00:02:38.110 --> 00:02:40.484
Abort mission. We return back to base.

16
00:02:42.276 --> 00:02:45.275
Take command.
Detain Richards and proceed as ordered.

17
00:02:46.026 --> 00:02:47.942
Richards, what the fuck are you doing?

18
00:02:48.026 --> 00:02:49.400
Shit. Let's get him!

19
00:02:58.318 --> 00:03:01.275
- God damn it!
- Shit, we're pitching over!

20
00:03:02.651 --> 00:03:04.734
I got it! I got control!

21
00:03:07.069 --> 00:03:09.485
They said detain him. Don't drop him.

22
00:03:16.486 --> 00:03:18.943
Richards, you're gonna fry for this.

23
00:03:19.568 --> 00:03:21.734
And I'll see you in hell.

24
00:03:34.944 --> 00:03:37.068
Come on, keep digging.

25
00:03:38.319 --> 00:03:40.859
- What's the holdup?
- This one's had it.

26
00:03:42.152 --> 00:03:44.026
Watch the detonator.

27
00:03:46.610 --> 00:03:49.734
Get that garbage out of here. Move!

28
00:04:51.945 --> 00:04:54.361
Hey, Charley,
did you see The Running Man last night?

29
00:04:54.445 --> 00:04:57.236
I never miss it. I even won 500 bucks.

30
00:04:58.403 --> 00:05:00.153
You lucky bastard.

31
00:05:00.945 --> 00:05:04.402
Work crew coming through.
Prisoner transfer to post.

32
00:05:04.486 --> 00:05:05.986
Okay. Hang on.

33
00:05:06.070 --> 00:05:09.153
Lenny, this is the East Perimeter.
Fresh meat just got here.

34
00:05:09.570 --> 00:05:10.944
Shut down the deadline.

35
00:05:11.029 --> 00:05:13.944
Affirmative. Shutting down now.
Stand clear.

36
00:05:15.987 --> 00:05:18.028
Access code pending.

37
00:05:19.237 --> 00:05:21.652
Verified. Perimeter deactivated.

38
00:05:21.737 --> 00:05:23.402
Sonic deadline is down.

39
00:05:24.070 --> 00:05:26.320
- Sonic deadline is down.
- Okay, assholes, move it. Move it.

40
00:05:26.403 --> 00:05:28.028
Let's go. Let's go!

41
00:05:28.112 --> 00:05:31.361
Get out the lead or lose your head.
Come on!

42
00:05:48.113 --> 00:05:51.361
East Perimeter here.
New prisoners are all in compound.

43
00:05:51.446 --> 00:05:52.445
We're clear.

44
00:05:52.529 --> 00:05:54.778
Affirmative. Activating deadline.

45
00:05:56.404 --> 00:05:57.987
What are you looking at? Get out of here.

46
00:05:58.071 --> 00:06:02.321
Sonic deadline is up. Sonic deadline is up.

47
00:06:02.821 --> 00:06:07.778
Prisoner restraint collars armed.
Prisoner restraint collars armed.

48
00:06:40.196 --> 00:06:41.903
Give you a lift?

49
