- I did. 653...

52
00:06:55.822 --> 00:06:57.280
Shit! It's not working.

53
00:07:01.281 --> 00:07:03.613
- You're a hell of an actor, Laughlin.
- Who was acting?

54
00:07:03.697 --> 00:07:05.446
Well, you're still alive, aren't you?

55
00:07:08.905 --> 00:07:10.654
- Repeat that code.
- Okay.

56
00:07:15.239 --> 00:07:18.196
Weiss, what's the holdup? Come on!

57
00:07:18.281 --> 00:07:20.362
The linking computer's denying the code.

58
00:07:23.031 --> 00:07:25.155
It must be the walls in here
blocking the signal.

59
00:07:25.239 --> 00:07:28.071
- It's not happening.
- Then we try it outside. Move!

60
00:07:36.822 --> 00:07:39.030
Hurry up! Let's go! Come on!

61
00:07:39.197 --> 00:07:40.738
Get out of the way. Move!

62
00:07:41.822 --> 00:07:43.696
Open the gates! Open the gates!

63
00:07:48.864 --> 00:07:50.196
Go ahead! Do it!

64
00:07:50.281 --> 00:07:52.738
Shut off the deadline
or we all lose our heads!

65
00:08:04.115 --> 00:08:07.031
The system's locked.
Must be an encryption lockout.

66
00:08:07.115 --> 00:08:08.323
Damn!

67
00:08:09.906 --> 00:08:13.447
Perimeter deactivated.
Perimeter deactivated.

68
00:08:13.531 --> 00:08:16.989
- All right! All right!
- Sonic deadline is down.

69
00:08:17.073 --> 00:08:19.989
- Prisoner restraint collars disarmed.
- Chico! Amigo!

70
00:08:20.073 --> 00:08:23.905
Chico! Come back! The deadline's still up.

71
00:08:24.948 --> 00:08:27.822
He's not going to make it.
That collar's going to blow.

72
00:08:27.906 --> 00:08:28.947
Sonic deadline is up.

73
00:08:29.032 --> 00:08:30.405
Chico!

74
00:08:32.740 --> 00:08:34.655
Prisoner restraint collars armed.

75
