What's the number one television show
in the whole wide world?

93
00:10:18.241 --> 00:10:21.324
- The Running Man!
- Yes!

94
00:10:21.407 --> 00:10:23.531
Yes, it's The Running Man.

95
00:10:23.616 --> 00:10:27.616
Four hundred square blocks of danger,
destruction, demolition, and...

96
00:10:27.700 --> 00:10:29.991
You guys want to buy a hot stereo?

97
00:10:30.075 --> 00:10:33.199
- Stevie.
- Laughlin. Glad you guys made it.

98
00:10:33.284 --> 00:10:36.657
...unstoppable network stalkers
give criminals,

99
00:10:36.742 --> 00:10:40.490
